## Workflow Recommendations

1. **Start with `/grill-me` or `/grill-with-docs`** before any major feature — align on intent before coding.
2. **Use `/tdd`** for red-green-refactor when implementing logic.
3. **Run `/diagnose`** when hitting hard bugs.
4. **Use `/to-prd` then `/to-issues`** to break work into vertical slices.
5. **Run `/improve-codebase-architecture`** every few days to prevent ball-of-mud.

